        <text>
            <body>
                <p>Ego <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324588" xml:id="d1e169162">Henricus, Dei gratia
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#319548" xml:id="d1e169164">Eduensis</placeName>
                        episcopus</persName>, posterorum memorie presenti scripto mandare disposui
                    qualiter terminate sint querele que inter <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e169168">Fonteneti</orgName> monachos et <persName key="d1e30159" xml:id="d1e169171">duos fratres Johannem</persName> et <persName key="d1e30165" xml:id="d1e169174">Renerium qui de Sancta Columba dicuntur
                        exorte fuerant</persName>. Monachi ab antiquo pastura <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324356" xml:id="d1e169177">Saigniaci</placeName> pro sua
                    utebantur, asserentes pasturas <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324479" xml:id="d1e169181">Aringiarum</placeName> et <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324335" xml:id="d1e169184">Ville Presbiteri</placeName>, <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324451" xml:id="d1e169187">Flaciaci</placeName> quoque et
                        <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324356" xml:id="d1e169190">Saigniaci</placeName>
                    esse communes. Supradicti vero fratres hoc denegabant. Tandem igitur ex
                    utriusque partis consensu tres legitimi viri designati sunt : <persName key="d1e30171" xml:id="d1e169193">Rainaldus major <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324421" xml:id="d1e169195">Buxiaci</placeName>, <persName key="d1e30178" xml:id="d1e169198">Milonis</persName> filius</persName>,
                        <persName key="d1e30184" xml:id="d1e169202">Milo <persName key="d1e30190" xml:id="d1e169204">Fulcuini</persName> filius</persName>, <persName key="d1e30196" xml:id="d1e169209">Martinus, nepos <persName key="d1e30202" xml:id="d1e169211">Lamberti de Monte</persName>
                    </persName>, quorum juramento presens <app>
                        <lem>controversia</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#C" type="omis"/>
                    </app> finiretur. Tres itaque isti super altare <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324356" xml:id="d1e169219">Saigniaci</placeName> juraverunt pasturas quas prediximus
                    sicut monachi asserebant esse communes. Cui sacramento affuerunt <persName key="d1e30208" xml:id="d1e169222">Walcherus presbiter</persName>, <persName key="d1e30215" xml:id="d1e169225">Rogerus <addName>Mechinus</addName>
                    </persName> qui jurantium manus tenuit, <persName key="d1e30221" xml:id="d1e169230">Wiardus Oliverii</persName>, <persName key="d1e30227" xml:id="d1e169234">Willelmus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324475" xml:id="d1e169236">Marmania</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30233" xml:id="d1e169239">Willelmus
                            <addName>Huldrei</addName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30239" xml:id="d1e169244">Girardus prepositus
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324459" xml:id="d1e169246">Grinionis</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30245" xml:id="d1e169249">Wido
                            <addName>Marinus</addName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30252" xml:id="d1e169254">Andreas <addName>
                            <foreign>Casarz</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName> et multi alii. Item querela altera erat inter eos de pratis ultra
                        <geogName xml:id="d1e169260">Brainam</geogName> versus <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324459" xml:id="d1e169264">Grinionem</placeName> et terra citra
                        <geogName xml:id="d1e169267">Brainam</geogName> que <persName key="d1e30258" xml:id="d1e169270">Robertus predictorum militum pater</persName> et prius
                    monachis impigneraverat et postea in elemosinam dederat. Quam elemosinam duo
                    illi predicti fratres nec a patre suo factam nec a se unquam laudatam fuisse
                    dicebant. Et hanc ergo elemosinam a patre suo factam recognoverunt et sicut
                    facta fuerat laudaverunt. Item commutationem terrarum quam fecerant monachi et
                        <persName key="d1e30264" xml:id="d1e169273">Robertus pater
                        ipsorum</persName> tempore quo terra erat in manu <persName key="d1e30270" xml:id="d1e169276">Havini de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324415" xml:id="d1e169278">
                            <foreign>Blasi</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName> quam prius infirmare temptaverant ratam habuerunt et gratanter
                    terram quam monachi pro commutatione dederant susceperunt. Item pro debito
                    quodam <num>vi</num> librarum quod monachi ab ipsis repetebant, terram eis in
                    monte sub <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325260" xml:id="d1e169286">Cumba
                        Radulphi</placeName> dederunt, que a monachis grate suscepta est, ita tamen
                    ut si quis super terra illa calumpniam<app>
                        <lem>
                            <witEnd wit="#B"/>
                        </lem>
                    </app> eis moverit aut predicti fratres calumpniam extingant aut aliam terram
                    monachis que non minus grate suscipiatur restituant. Hec omnia sicut in presenti
                    pagina continentur predicti duo fratres, <persName key="d1e30276" xml:id="d1e169293">Johannes</persName> et <persName key="d1e30282" xml:id="d1e169296">Renerius</persName>, ante <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324475" xml:id="d1e169299">ecclesiam Marmanie</placeName> coram multis testibus
                    retractari fecerunt et sicut retracta fuerant ad utilitatem <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e169302">Fontenetensis</orgName> domus a se
                    deinceps imperpetuum conservanda allatis sacrosanctis reliquiis juraverunt. Unde
                    sunt testes <persName key="d1e30289" xml:id="d1e169306">Odo
                    presbiter</persName>, <persName key="d1e30295" xml:id="d1e169309">Viardus de
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325023" xml:id="d1e169311">Saneveyo</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30301" xml:id="d1e169314">Bernardus
                            <addName>Nariodi</addName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30307" xml:id="d1e169319">Osmundus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324341" xml:id="d1e169321">Plaaneto</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30313" xml:id="d1e169324">Robertus <addName>
                            <foreign>Gorruns</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30319" xml:id="d1e169330">Christianus <addName>
                            <foreign>Allauz</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName>. Hec omnia laudavit <persName key="d1e30326" xml:id="d1e169337">Petrus frater ipsorum</persName> et sicut fratres sui de fide super hoc
                    negotio <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e169340">Fontenetensibus</orgName> conservanda juraverant, etiam ipse juravit.
                    Laudavit quoque <persName key="d1e30332" xml:id="d1e169343">mater eorum
                        Luca</persName> et due <persName key="d1e30338" xml:id="d1e169346">sorores
                        eorumdem, Adelina</persName> et <persName key="d1e30344" xml:id="d1e169349">Maria</persName>. Laudationis hujus tam <persName key="d1e30350" xml:id="d1e169352">matris</persName> scilicet quam <persName key="d1e30356" xml:id="d1e169356">Petri</persName> et duarum sororum testes sunt <persName key="d1e30363" xml:id="d1e169359">Vido de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324374" xml:id="d1e169361">
                            <foreign>Venerre</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30369" xml:id="d1e169365">Viardus</persName> et
                        <persName key="d1e30375" xml:id="d1e169368">Oliverius fratres</persName>,
                        <persName key="d1e30381" xml:id="d1e169371">
                        <sic>Hu</sic> de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325036" xml:id="d1e169375">Turre</placeName>
                    </persName>. Sed et juramenti quod fecit <persName key="d1e30387" xml:id="d1e169378">Petrus</persName> testes sunt idem <persName key="d1e30393" xml:id="d1e169382">Wido de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324374" xml:id="d1e169384">
                            <foreign>Venerre</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30400" xml:id="d1e169388">Petrus
                            <addName>Uldrei</addName>
                    </persName>. Laudavit etiam universa hec <persName key="d1e30406" xml:id="d1e169393">Luca, <persName key="d1e30412" xml:id="d1e169395">Johannis</persName> uxor</persName>. Unde sunt testes <persName key="d1e30418" xml:id="d1e169399">Willermus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324441" xml:id="d1e169401">Dreiis</placeName> tunc
                        prior</persName> et <persName key="d1e30424" xml:id="d1e169405">Humbertus de
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324445" xml:id="d1e169407">Schanneto</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30430" xml:id="d1e169410">Aubertus filius
                        ejus</persName> et <persName key="d1e30437" xml:id="d1e169414">Gaufridus
                        ejusdem generi</persName>, et <persName key="d1e30443" xml:id="d1e169417">Gertrudis <persName key="d1e30449" xml:id="d1e169419">ipsius
                            Luce</persName> mater</persName>.</p>
                <p>Dederunt autem monachi pro hiis omnibus de beneficio suo <persName key="d1e30455" xml:id="d1e169425">Johanni</persName> solidos <num>lxx</num>
                    <hi rend="superscript">ta</hi> et <persName key="d1e30461" xml:id="d1e169433">Renerio</persName>
                    <num>lx</num> solidos, <persName key="d1e30467" xml:id="d1e169438">Petro</persName> et <persName key="d1e30474" xml:id="d1e169442">duabus
                        sororibus</persName> solidos <hi rend="smallcaps">v,</hi>
                    <persName key="d1e30480" xml:id="d1e169447">Luce uxori <persName key="d1e30486" xml:id="d1e169449">Johannis</persName>
                    </persName> vacam unam cum vitulo.</p>
                <p>Hec autem omnia petentibus tam monachis <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e169454">Fonteneti</orgName> quam illis duobus fratribus <persName key="d1e30492" xml:id="d1e169457">Johanne</persName> et <persName key="d1e30498" xml:id="d1e169460">Renerio</persName> et astantibus sub
                    audientia nostra legi precepimus et sigillo nostro confirmata munivimus,
                    interdicentes sub anathematis comminatione ne quis ista quolibet modo temerare
                    presumat.</p>
            </body>
